---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FountainFormat — The Screenplay Markup Language">
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="stars"></div>
        <div class="glow"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>Write screenplays in plain text</h1>
          <p class="tagline">Fountain is the open markup language for screenwriters. Human-readable, software-agnostic, future-proof. Created by John August and Stu Maschwitz.</p>
          <a href="https://coffeedraft.com" class="cta">Try CoffeeDraft Editor</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="demo">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Example</h2>
        <h3>Plain text becomes formatted screenplay</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-grid">
        <div class="demo-col">
          <div class="demo-label">Fountain source</div>
          <pre class="fountain-code">INT. COFFEE SHOP - DAY

A quiet corner. Rain on glass.

ANNA
(hesitant)
Is this seat taken?

MARCUS
It is now.</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-col">
          <div class="demo-label">Rendered output</div>
          <div class="rendered">
            <div class="scene">INT. COFFEE SHOP - DAY</div>
            <div class="action">A quiet corner. Rain on glass.</div>
            <div class="character">ANNA</div>
            <div class="paren">(hesitant)</div>
            <div class="dialogue">Is this seat taken?</div>
            <div class="character">MARCUS</div>
            <div class="dialogue">It is now.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Fountain</h2>
        <h3>No lock-in. No special software. Just text.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <h4>Plain text</h4>
          <p>Write in any editor. Notepad, VS Code, iA Writer—anything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h4>Portable</h4>
          <p>Your scripts are .fountain files. Open them anywhere, forever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h4>Readable</h4>
          <p>Looks like a screenplay even as raw text. No cryptic markup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="syntax-preview">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Quick Reference</h2>
        <h3>Core syntax at a glance</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="syntax-list">
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>INT. LOCATION</code><span>Scene heading</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>CHARACTER</code><span>All caps, own line</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>(parenthetical)</code><span>Wrapped in parens</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>Dialogue text</code><span>Lines after character</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>Action lines</code><span>Regular paragraphs</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>> FADE OUT.</code><span>Transitions</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>*italic* **bold**</code><span>Emphasis</span></div>
        <div class="syntax-item"><code>===</code><span>Page break</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="origin">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Origin</h2>
        <h3>Built by screenwriters, for screenwriters</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Fountain was created in 2011 by <a href="https://johnaugust.com">John August</a> (Big Fish, Charlie's Angels) and <a href="https://prolost.com">Stu Maschwitz</a> (visual effects artist and software developer). They merged two projects—Scrippets and Screenplay Markdown—into a single open standard.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main { width: 100%; }

  section {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-top: none;
  }

  .hero-card {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c1929 0%, #0d1f2d 50%, #0a1a28 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  :root.light .hero-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe 0%, #f0fdfa 50%, #ecfeff 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.2) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 40% at 30% 20%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  :root.light .glow {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .stars {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background-image: 
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 10% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 30% 10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 50% 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 70% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 90% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  :root.light .stars { display: none; }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .cta:hover { background: #115e59; }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .demo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--card);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .demo-col {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .demo-col:first-child {
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .demo-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .fountain-code {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 12pt;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .rendered {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 12pt;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .scene { color: var(--white); }
  .action { color: var(--text); margin: 0.75rem 0; }
  .character { color: var(--white); text-align: center; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .paren { color: var(--text-dim); text-align: center; font-size: 11pt; }
  .dialogue { color: var(--text); text-align: center; max-width: 65%; margin: 0 auto; }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .feature {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature h4 {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .syntax-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .syntax-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .syntax-item code {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    background: var(--card);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .syntax-item span {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .origin p {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .origin a {
    color: var(--accent-light);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .origin a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>